FBIS3-14333 "drnes058_n_94001" FBIS-NES-94-058 Document Type:Daily Report 23 Mar 1994 LEBANON Wrapup of Israeli Military Activity in South Lebanon Artillery Brought In NC2303182394 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1630 GMT 23 Mar 94 NC2303182394 Beirut Radio Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] According to reports received from the south, the Israeli occupation forces have brought in 15 pieces of artillery across the al-Kharadli Bridge inside the border strip and deployed them south of the Balat township. AFP cited sources in the port of Tyre as saying that the Israeli navy kidnapped seven Lebanese fishermen after firing on their boats inside Lebanon's territorial water. The sources added that the kidnappers towed the fishermen's boats to the port of Nahariyya.
